E-commerce Platform
Features:

User Authentication: Implement user registration and login functionality.
Product Listings: Display products with sorting and filtering options.
Shopping Cart: Allow users to add/remove items from their cart.
Checkout Process: Integrate payment gateways like Stripe or PayPal.
Admin Panel: For managing products, categories, and user orders.
Technologies:

Frontend: React, Redux (for state management), React Router (for navigation)
Backend: Node.js with Express (or any backend you prefer)
Database: MongoDB or Firebase
Styling: CSS-in-JS libraries like Styled Components or CSS frameworks like Bootstrap
